vim <filename>
open vim

i
insert mode

Esc
exit insert mode

:w 
save

:wq
save and quit

:x
save and quit

:q
quit and unsaved

I
insert at beginning of line

yy
copy

p
paste

dd 
delete a line

/ backward search n 
This is used for finding the next occurrence.

 / backward search N
This is somehow related to the above command but it searches in the opposite direction.
